\x938.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/9061728" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2719511&amp;issue-id=355069&amp;journal-id=3817&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Pediatr+Emerg+Care&amp;title=Aerobic+and+anaerobic+microbiology+of+bacterial+tracheitis+in+children&amp;author=I+Brook&amp;volume=13&amp;publication_year=1997&amp;pages=16-8&amp;pmid=9061728&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2719511&amp;issue-id=355069&amp;journal-id=3817&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="b14-pch09021">14. <span class="element-citation">Brook I. Pneumonia in mechanically ventilated children. <span><span class="ref-journal">Scand J Infect Dis. </span>1995;<span class="ref-vol">27</span>:619\xe2\x80\x9322.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/8685643" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2719511&amp;issue-id=355069&amp;journal-id=3817&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Scand+J+Infect+Dis&amp;title=Pneumonia+in+mechanically+ventilated+children&amp;author=I+Brook&amp;volume=27&amp;publication_year=1995&amp;pages=619-22&amp;pmid=8685643&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2719511&amp;issue-id=355069&amp;journal-id=3817&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div></div></div></div><!--post-content--></div>\n            \n            \n        \n            \n        </div>\n        <!-- Book content -->\n    </div>\n    \n    <div id="rightcolumn" class="four_col col last">\n        <!-- Custom content above discovery portlets -->\n        <div class="col6">\n            \n        </div>\n   